des:
Listen to 97.7 1330 AM MeTV FM features a unique mix of timeless and memorable music incorporating a wide variety of classic hits, deep tracks, and softer sounds spanning several decades of popular music on your Amazon devices. 

Once you've enabled the skill, saying "Alexa, play kvol" gets you right in. 

Find out what else you can do by saying "Alexa, ask kvol for help"
